Lactalis Ingredients' premium milk minerals targeted towards personal care products and animal feed segments highlight its versatility and commitment to meeting diverse consumer needs. The company's extensive product range and sustainable practices contribute to its market success and sustainable growth. FrieslandCampina's diverse offerings in milk minerals cater to different market segments and applications, showcasing its adaptability and agility in responding to market trends and consumer preferences.

